Ross Bagley https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ross_Bagley 0 Ross Elliot Bagley (born December 5, 1988) is an American former actor and comedian he is best known for his role as Nicky Banks in The Fresh Prince of Bel-Air as well as Dylan Dubrow-Hiller in Independence Day.
